[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12420] fixed a bug by canonicalizing XDG_CONFIG_HOME before comparing to config_dir()
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12419] added BufWriter to ChildStdin on the plugin interface
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12418] fixed deadlock on PluginCustomValue drop
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12417] fixed some of the tests in 
``tests::shell``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12409] improved handling of custom values in plugin examples
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12394] fixed #12391: mkdir uses process startup directory instead of current script directory
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12392] fixed testing.nu import of std log
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12341] made drop notification timing for plugin custom values more consistent
