[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12401] tweaked release workflow after 
``0.92.1``
 lessons
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12385] made the default config conservative about clipboard
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12381] bumped 
``crate-ci/typos``
 and fixed typos
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12349] bumped the Nu version for 
``0.92.0``
 release
merelymyself 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12393] prevented 
``select``
 (negative number) from hanging shell
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12378] prevented parser from parsing variables as units
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12359] made 
``view source``
 more robust
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12342] made auto-cd check for permissions
